{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"964ab93aa2","title":"周恩来陈伯达接见福建赴京两派代表达成的四个协议","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"832407b25d","index":0,"year":1967,"month":8,"day":10,"articleId":"964ab93aa2","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"大联合","id":"18bf6a78fe","type":"主题"},{"name":"周恩来","id":"523bb79e8f","type":"人物"},{"name":"周总理","id":"838b5f2c9d","type":"人物"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"造反运动和派别斗争","id":"d48f0ea3e8","type":"主题"},{"name":"陈伯达","id":"e46e45351b","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"48606ca4e5","name":"陈伯达"},{"id":"7a99cebe4e","name":"周恩来"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"3c09b86609","type":"title","text":"周恩来陈伯达接见福建赴京两派代表达成的四个协议","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"964ab93aa2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4b8c195dab","type":"paragraph","text":"〖八月十日晚至八月十一日晨，和八月十一日晚－八月十二日晨，周总理、陈伯达同志在西苑旅社连续接见福建赴京两派代表。两派代表达成四次协议。〗","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"964ab93aa2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bb0cfd401b","type":"paragraph","text":"第一个协议：8.11  1时","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"964ab93aa2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bd4bf0b002","type":"paragraph","text":"双方毫无条件地，毫无保留地立即停止武斗，立即释放全部互抓人员，必须在11 日中午十二点前释放完毕，要我们立即执行，其他问题在继续协议中。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"964ab93aa2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"938e10eed0","type":"paragraph","text":"福建革命造反委员会：陈力生、潘家驹；“八二九”：庄志鹏、余映辉","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"964ab93aa2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4c911fad34","type":"paragraph","text":"第二个协议：8.11  10时","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"964ab93aa2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"44225ac29c","type":"paragraph","text":"放人后革造会在三小时内撤出华侨大厅，及其周围的全部人员，回到原地，原驻华侨大厅的“八二九”等八个总部在半月内全部撤出华侨大厅，另迁均为朴素的新地。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"964ab93aa2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8379804275","type":"paragraph","text":"“八二九”等组织原驻的其他楼厅，立即按照艰苦朴素的原则自行调查，革造会原驻的楼厅也应按艰苦朴素的原则自行调整。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"964ab93aa2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"dd529e3f42","type":"paragraph","text":"第三个协议：8.12 晨","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"964ab93aa2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5f4d91c987","type":"paragraph","text":"双方不得以任何借口任何方式挑动农民进城参加武斗，双方坚决反对挑动农民进城参加武斗，进城的应立即必须回原村。","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"964ab93aa2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d1157ccddb","type":"paragraph","text":"必须绝对禁止任何人，任何机关利用任何借口或用所谓老区农民进城，挑动农民进城，挑动武斗的幕后策划者应负担全部责任和一切后果。","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"964ab93aa2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5d3a297b62","type":"paragraph","text":"上山下乡青年都不得借口进城，已经进城的都必须尽快回原地抓革命促生产，坚决执行中央723关于禁止农民进城参加武斗的通知。","index":11,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"964ab93aa2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f661723f5a","type":"paragraph","text":"第四个协议：8.12  8时","index":12,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"964ab93aa2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"99c43aa30c","type":"paragraph","text":"1．不得以任何借口任何形式抓打搜，拘留不同观点的群众。","index":13,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"964ab93aa2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"05a081fd25","type":"paragraph","text":"2．在协议达成三天后停止使用广播车，撤消在街头的广播站。","index":14,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"964ab93aa2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f5401c5069","type":"paragraph","text":"3．不得撕毁、涂改、复盖不同观点大字报、标语，不准搞一言堂，保证四大。","index":15,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"964ab93aa2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fc726d36b2","type":"paragraph","text":"4．互不围攻，各方自动拆除武斗工事（包括街头制高点）。","index":16,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"964ab93aa2","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}